headline: Reflecting On Patient Monitoring Stocks’ Q1 Earnings: Masimo (NASDAQ:MASI)
summary: The end of an earnings season can be a great time to discover new stocks and assess how companies are handling the current business environment. Let’s take a look at how Masimo (NASDAQ:MASI) and the rest of the patient monitoring stocks fared in Q1.
